FBIS3-58252 "drweu007_i_94004" FBIS-WEU-94-007 Document Type:Daily Report 11 Jan 1994 FRANCE Calls For Nuclear Test Resumption AU1001102994 Paris AFP in English 1004 GMT 10 Jan 94 AU1001102994 Paris AFP Language: English Article Type:BFN [Excerpt] Paris, Jan 10 (AFP) -- France ought to resume nuclear weapons testing as soon as possible, Defence Minister Francois Leotard said here Monday [10 January], contradicting President Francois Mitterrand. Speaking in a radio interview, Leotard said the precise reason for resuming tests was to acquire simulation techniques. [passage omitted]
